// POST /api/oauth/token - OAuth token exchange proxy
//
// Proxies authorization_code and refresh_token grant requests to OAuth providers,
// injecting the client_secret server-side so it never ships in client code.
//
// Supports multiple client IDs per provider (e.g., Google friction-free + verified-full),
